  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Unique Vehicle]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This vehicle is a huge flying sword, with exaggerated size and tough style, making it an unparalleled flying vehicle. Young man, take your seat and get ready to enter the battle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Powerful Set]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The set of equipment is the most distinctive gameplay feature of this game. It enables one to most intuitively perceive the changes of the character. The set offers various attribute boosts, unique passive skills, and four extremely powerful active skills. Put on the set and charge ahead bravely!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Handsome Skills]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The professional role not only possesses multiple skills, but also some skills are specially designed to be extremely handsome! The damage output is also very powerful. Battle! Cool! Battle! Cool! Battle! Cool!!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Hardcore-style melee weapons]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This melee weapon has a tough and rugged appearance, rich basic attribute panels, and a unique melee weapon combat MOD. The weapon can be equipped with various combat MODs, and it has a limit on the number of slots. However, each combat MOD can significantly enhance the attributes of this weapon! Choose the combat MOD that best suits your own style for your melee weapon!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Various Plugins with Different Attributes]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Armor, the core gameplay feature of this game, features a modular system for different parts of the armor. Each part can accommodate a limited number of modules, but each module offers extremely powerful attribute boosts. You can directly feel the significant attribute enhancements brought by the modules. With modules installed, you become stronger and more courageous!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[The powerful enemy faction]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the difficulty increases, your enemies will become stronger. Meanwhile, the rewards will also rise accordingly. Kill the enemies and you will obtain more rewards to make your character stronger!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Game Type]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a third-person action combat game. You will play as a [Pioneer] and take part in the game on the land of Zhongshu. By completing tasks and killing enemies, you can obtain resources and enhance your character's strength. Enjoy the battles to your heart's content!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Author's Note]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was developed and tested by the author alone. When I was in primary school and was pulled into the arcade game hall by my classmates, I fell in love with games from then on. I am extremely passionate about games. Therefore, through continuous iterations, I finally made this game. I wish everyone a pleasant gaming experience~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Official QQ Group]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Front Runner]: 206879554</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Unique Vehicle]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/8057d001ccc5ffd83c3b6fcccf1ae047.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This vehicle is a huge flying sword, with exaggerated size and tough style, making it an unparalleled flying vehicle. Young man, take your seat and get ready to enter the battle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Powerful Set]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/9f75f026e653884ced40223c922666c0.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The set of equipment is the most distinctive gameplay feature of this game. It enables one to most intuitively perceive the changes of the character. The set offers various attribute boosts, unique passive skills, and four extremely powerful active skills. Put on the set and charge ahead bravely!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Handsome Skills]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/4e758ef1d764381fb9c8b3d75405e478.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The professional role not only possesses multiple skills, but also some skills are specially designed to be extremely handsome! The damage output is also very powerful. Battle! Cool! Battle! Cool! Battle! Cool!!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Hardcore-style melee weapons]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f04a97c6978d15b209a1b438720ffe8b.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This melee weapon has a tough and rugged appearance, rich basic attribute panels, and a unique melee weapon combat MOD. The weapon can be equipped with various combat MODs, and it has a limit on the number of slots. However, each combat MOD can significantly enhance the attributes of this weapon! Choose the combat MOD that best suits your own style for your melee weapon!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Various Plugins with Different Attributes]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/f62cd35633fa9eb931ad2384b82e7c09.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Armor, the core gameplay feature of this game, features a modular system for different parts of the armor. Each part can accommodate a limited number of modules, but each module offers extremely powerful attribute boosts. You can directly feel the significant attribute enhancements brought by the modules. With modules installed, you become stronger and more courageous!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[The powerful enemy faction]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.poster.avif?t=1755724750\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.webm?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3687110/extras/16e3edf89601d4cdae74fe374dbbf606.mp4?t=1755724750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the difficulty increases, your enemies will become stronger. Meanwhile, the rewards will also rise accordingly. Kill the enemies and you will obtain more rewards to make your character stronger!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>[Game Type]</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a third-person action combat game. You will play as a [Pioneer] and take part in the game on the land of Zhongshu. By completing tasks and killing enemies, you can obtain resources and enhance your character's strength. Enjoy the battles to your heart's content!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Author's Note]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was developed and tested by the author alone. When I was in primary school and was pulled into the arcade game hall by my classmates, I fell in love with games from then on. I am extremely passionate about games. Therefore, through continuous iterations, I finally made this game. I wish everyone a pleasant gaming experience~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>[Official QQ Group]</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Front Runner]: 206879554</p>",
